title: Israeli protesters call for PM Netanyahu's resignation
text:
Israeli protesters call for PM Netanyahu's resignation 8:25pm IST - 00:59 
Demonstrators gather in Tel Aviv calling on Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu to resign after police recommended that he be charged with bribery. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
